i3 Window Manager Basic Key Bindings - for all key bindings check ~/.config/i3/config
Windows key or Super key = Mod4
To open this cheat sheet, press Mod4 + z and Mod4 + Shift + q to close it

# Open programs
Mod4 + Return - Open a terminal (Return is also known as Intro or Enter)
Mod4 + n - Open nitrogen (For change wallpaper)
Mod4 + p - Open pcmanfm (File Manager)
Mod4 + x - Open lxappearance (For changing GTK themes)
Mod4 + m - Open Telegram
Mod4 + d - Open dmenu (A program launcher)
Mod4 + t - Open i3 & alacritty theme selector (with dmenu)

# Navigation
Mod4 + 1-9 - Switch to workspaces 1-9
(Using arrow keys)
Mod4 + Left - Change focus to left
Mod4 + Right - Change focus to right
Mod4 + Up - Change focus to up
Mod4 + Down - Change focus to down
Mod4 + Shift + Left - Move focused window to left
Mod4 + Shift + Right - Move focused window to right
Mod4 + Shift + Up - Move focused window to up
Mod4 + Shift + Down - Move focused window to down

# Window Manager Control
Mod4 + Shift + q - Close focused window
Mod4 + Shift + r - Restart i3wm
Mod4 + Shift + c - Reload i3wm config file
Mod4 + Shift + e - Exit i3wm

